Changes in release 1.01
* RCS Symbolic version V1_01
* User defined operators (UDOs) added
* INITIAL declaration support
* More bugs fixed and kroc output support

Changes in release 1.0
* RCS Symbolic version V1_0
* Brought under GNU configure system
* No semantic changes - just configuration and cosmetic changes where
  necssary to add portability.

Changes in version for KROC 0.8beta
* RCS Symbolic version V0_8_beta

Baseline system
* RCS Symbolic version V1
  baseline for sparc, alpha, alpha native & linux
